OL,3,CTributes at gates as school mourns
OL,4,Cdeath of 'devoted' head teacher
OL,6,FTributes have been placed outside a
OL,7,Fgrammar school mourning the tragic
OL,8,Floss of its beloved headteacher.
OL,10,FThe long-serving head of Stretford
OL,11,FGrammar School in Trafford, Michael
OL,12,FMullins, was killed in a collision as
OL,13,Fhe cycled in Altrincham on the evening
OL,14,Fof Monday, 20 April.
OL,16,FThe 56-year-old, a father and
OL,17,Fgrandfather, had been the school's
OL,18,Fheadteacher for 17 years and lived
OL,19,Fwith his family in Weaverham,
OL,20,FNorthwich.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
