OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776931533
OL,3,CTributes at gates as school mourns
OL,4,Cdeath of 'devoted' head teacher
OL,6,FThe school was closed on Tuesday as a
OL,7,Fmark of respect, but is understood to
OL,8,Fhave reopened for pupils on Wednesday.
OL,10,FFloral tributes in memory of Mr
OL,11,FMullins have been attached to the
OL,12,Fschool's gates, together with a shirt
OL,13,Ffrom Stretford-based Longford Park
OL,14,FJunior Football Club.
OL,16,FIn a statement posted to social media
OL,17,Fon Wednesday, the club said it was
OL,18,F'deeply saddened' at the shock news,
OL,19,Fcalling him 'an advocate for
OL,20,Fgrassroots football and our community'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776931533
OL,3,CTributes at gates as school mourns
OL,4,Cdeath of 'devoted' head teacher
OL,6,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP)
OL,7,Fconfirmed Mr Mullins' bike was hit by
OL,8,Fa car at around 6pm on Paddock Lane in
OL,9,FAltrincham on Monday. He tragically
OL,10,Fdied of his injuries, the force said.
OL,12,FIn a statement issued through GMP
OL,13,Fafter his death, his family said: "Our
OL,14,Floving Dad, husband, Brother-in-law,
OL,15,F'Diddy', Uncle, Son in law, passed
OL,16,Faway last night after being knocked
OL,17,Foff his bike.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776931533
OL,3,CTributes at gates as school mourns
OL,4,Cdeath of 'devoted' head teacher
OL,6,F"He was devoted to his family and our
OL,7,Flives will never be the same. A gap
OL,8,Fhas been left in our hearts and within
OL,9,Fhis role as a headteacher of Stretford
OL,10,FGrammar school.
OL,12,F"Our Dad gave us fantastic memories
OL,13,Fgrowing up including a trip getting
OL,14,Flost at night around Washington D.C
OL,15,Fbut it was in his role as a Grandad
OL,16,Fwhere he truly excelled. At this time
OL,17,Fthe family request privacy. Our love
OL,18,Fand memories of Michael will know no
OL,19,Flimits. We will love him forever, to
OL,20,FSaturn and beyond."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776931533
OL,3,CTributes at gates as school mourns
OL,4,Cdeath of 'devoted' head teacher
OL,6,FGMP said the vehicle involved in the
OL,7,Fcrash failed to stop, but four people,
OL,8,Fthree men and a woman, were later
OL,9,Farrested on suspicion of causing death
OL,10,Fby dangerous driving.
OL,12,FAll four remain in custody for
OL,13,Fquestioning, according to the last
OL,14,Fpolice update.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
