OL,3,CTributes at gates as school mourns
OL,4,Cdeath of 'devoted' head teacher
OL,6,FThe football club wrote on Facebook:
OL,7,F"As many of you will have heard about
OL,8,FMr Mullins, what you may not know is
OL,9,Fjust how great an advocate he was for
OL,10,Fgrassroots football and for our
OL,11,Fcommunity. For coming up to 10 years,
OL,12,Fhe welcomed our club with open arms
OL,13,Fand stood firmly behind everything we
OL,14,Fdo.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776931533
OL,3,CTributes at gates as school mourns
OL,4,Cdeath of 'devoted' head teacher
OL,6,F"No matter what barriers were put in
OL,7,Ffront of us, Mr Mullins would help
OL,8,Ftear them down so our children could
OL,9,Fget outside and play on that field.
OL,10,FHis belief in giving young people a
OL,11,Fsafe, positive place to play will
OL,12,Fleave a lasting legacy. His support,
OL,13,Fkindness, and dedication will never be
OL,14,Fforgotten.
OL,16,F"Our thoughts and heartfelt
OL,17,Fcondolences are with his family,
OL,18,Ffriends, and everyone at Stretford
OL,19,FGrammar School at this incredibly
OL,20,Fdifficult time."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
