CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776931533
OL,3,CTributes at gates as school mourns
OL,4,Cdeath of 'devoted' head teacher
OL,6,FPaying tribute, Stretford and Urmston
OL,7,FMP Andrew Western said: "I am shocked
OL,8,Fand truly saddened to hear the
OL,9,Fdevastating news of Mr Mullins' tragic
OL,10,Fdeath. My thoughts and condolences go
OL,11,Fout to the staff and students at
OL,13,FStretford Grammar, and above all to
OL,14,FMichael's family and friends.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776931533
OL,3,CTributes at gates as school mourns
OL,4,Cdeath of 'devoted' head teacher
OL,6,F"Michael was a lovely man and in the
OL,7,Fconversations we had it was clear that
OL,8,Fthe needs of the children in his care
OL,9,Fwere always at the heart of everything
OL,10,Fhe did. His loss will be felt deeply
OL,11,Fby all who knew him, here in the
OL,12,FStretford community and beyond."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
